title: FS2004 - feelThere PIC ERJ-135 BJ Legacy (full installer)
description:
TESTED

feelThere / Wilco&#039;s Embraer ERJ-135 Business Jet "Legacy" Pilot In Command

Full installer, including Service Pack 1 and serial !!!

h**p://www.feelthere.com/2005/legacy.html

Some features:

* HUD 
* WX Radar

* New FADEC modes 
* Nose wheel steering limiter above 40 kts

* New eye candy features 

Many thanks to B-52H and MoBig for uploading this add-on to a.b.w.f. !


Happy landings,
